Suǒyǐ rén yòu zěnme huì yǒu “zì xìng” ne?

332
00:38:52,320 --> 00:39:01,158
如果一个人犯错，也就是众生犯错，每个人都是同谋者！
When one man sins, we all share his sin, we are all accomplices
Rúguǒ yīgèrén fàncuò, yě jiùshì zhòngshēng fàncuò, měi gè rén dōu shì tóngmóu zhě!

333
00:39:10,360 --> 00:39:14,314
你是说杀人犯之所以成为杀人犯，也是非他的“自性”？
Are you saying that a killer doesn't have free will when he kills?
Nǐ shì shuō shārén fàn zhī suǒyǐ chéngwéi shārén fàn, yě shìfēi tā de “zì xìng”?

334
00:39:15,680 --> 00:39:17,591
他只是生于杀戳之家
He was conditioned to the act
Tā zhǐshì shēng yú shā chuō zhī jiā

335
00:39:18,080 --> 00:39:22,992
他杀了人，众生都有罪，大家都是同谋者
And when he kills, because we're all part of that sin we're all accomplices?
Tāshāle rén, zhòngshēng dōu yǒuzuì, dàjiā dōu shì tóngmóu zhě

336
00:39:24,120 --> 00:39:25,997
我没想过杀人犯
I wasn't thinking of killers
Wǒ méi xiǎngguò shārén fàn

337
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:40,356
就是看不到他的破绽
I found no proof
Jiùshì kàn bù dào tā de pòzhàn

338
00:39:41,240 --> 00:39:45,358
那你为何不放过他，他想做个好人
Then leave him alone, he's a reformed man
Nà nǐ wèihé bù fàngguò tā, tā xiǎng zuò gè hǎorén

339
00:39:46,560 --> 00:39:49,120
我们抓人不是要让他们做好人的
We're not here to reform criminals
Wǒmen zhuā rén bùshì yào ràng tāmen zuò hǎorén de

340
00:39:49,640 --> 00:39:51,039
那为了什么？
Then what's our purpose?
Nà wèile shénme?

341
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:53,953
为了法呀！
To serve the law
Wèile fǎ ya!

342
00:39:54,520 --> 00:40:00,076
如果法不能使一个人变成好人的话，那法又有什么用？
If the law doesn't help reform people, what good is it?
Rúguǒ fǎ bùnéng shǐ yīgè rén biàn chéng hǎorén dehuà, nà fǎ yòu yǒu shé me yòng?

343
00:40:00,200 --> 00:40:05,396
真正武功高强的人，可以开合穴道、控制他的性格
A true martial artist can control, the flow of his Qi and his mental state
Zhēnzhèng wǔgōng gāoqiáng de rén, kěyǐ kāi hé xuédào, kòngzhì tā dì xìnggé

344
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:10,789
你别以为杀人犯装得像个好人就是好人
He may appear to be a good man but he's still a killer
Nǐ bié yǐwéi shārén fàn zhuāng dé xiàng gè hǎorén jiùshì hǎorén

345
00:40:11,240 --> 00:40:12,593
你还是赶快去一趟荆州
Go to Lianzhou and dig around
Nǐ háishì gǎnkuài qù yī tàng jīngzhōu

346
00:40:13,200 --> 00:40:15,429
查明之后，回来告诉我
Once you get the information report back to me
Chá míng zhīhòu, huílái gàosù wǒ

347
00:40:16,120 --> 00:40:20,432
百九，你要小心啊，别忘了你的身子
Baijiu, take care of yourself, don't forget your condition
Bǎi jiǔ, nǐ yào xiǎoxīn a, bié wàngle nǐ de shēnzi

348
00:40:20,720 --> 00:40:23,234
别以为自己武功了不得
You can't actually fight
Bié yǐwéi zìjǐ wǔ gōng liǎo bùdé

349
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:24,955
什么意思？
What are you saying?
Shénme yìsi?

350
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:28,953
你不是说这个人武功高强嘛？
He might be a trained killer, you said so yourself
Nǐ bùshì shuō zhège rén wǔgōng gāoqiáng ma?

351
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:33,908
你是说…他会杀我灭口了？
You think...he's going to silence me?
Nǐ shì shuō…tā huì shā wǒ mièkǒule?

352
00:40:35,240 --> 00:40:37,515
总之你得小心点
Just be careful
Zǒngzhī nǐ dé xiǎoxīn diǎn

353
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:53,555
多吃一点  -嗯
Have some more
Duō chī yīdiǎn  -ń

354
00:40:58,440 --> 00:41:01,113
哎呀，你别光顾着自己吃，这有客人
Where're your manners? We have a guest
Āiyā, nǐ bié guānggùzhe zìjǐ chī, zhè yǒu kèrén

356
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:12,269
多夹一点呀，啊？多夹一点吧，多吃一点
Have some more, Have more
Duō jiā yīdiǎn ya, a? Duō jiā yīdiǎn ba, duō chī yīdiǎn

357
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:19,236
徐百九，你是…你是哪里人？
Xu Baijiu, where are you from?
Xúbǎijiǔ, nǐ shì…nǐ shì nǎlǐ rén?

358
00:41:21,680 --> 00:41:23,113
四川温江
Fucheng, Chaozhou
Sìchuān wēnjiāng

359
00:41:24,360 --> 00:41:26,590
不远呀，很近的
It's not far
Bù yuǎn ya, hěn jìn de

360
00:41:30,720 --> 00:41:35,312
听说你家乡在荆州啊，那是很远的地方哦
I hear your hometown is in Lianzhou, it's so far away
Tīng shuō nǐ jiāxiāng zài jīngzhōu a, nà shì hěn yuǎn dì dìfāng ó

361
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:41,718
你那么远跑到这里来，要不就是很喜欢这儿，要不就是很讨厌那儿
What brought you out here? You either love it here or hate where you come from
Nǐ nàme yuǎn pǎo dào zhèlǐ lái, yào bù jiùshì hěn xǐhuān zhè'er, yào bù jiùshì hěn tǎoyàn nà'er

362
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,558
我很喜欢这儿
Yes, I like it here
Wǒ hěn xǐhuān zhè'er

363
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:52,718
那你，你家不远的话，你是不是可以经常回去？
Fucheng is close, You must go home often?
Nà nǐ, nǐ jiā bù yuǎn dehuà, nǐ shì bùshì kěyǐ jīngcháng huíqù?

364
00:41:53,680 --> 00:41:55,636
我听说你们家那边气候很好的
I hear the weather there is nice
Wǒ tīng shuō nǐmen jiā nà biān qìhòu hěn hǎo de

365
00:41:55,760 --> 00:41:56,556
嗯
Well...
Ń

366
00:41:58,080 --> 00:42:03,432
家父仙游了，母亲另嫁，我就很少回去了
Since my father died and my mother remarried, I seldom visit
Jiāfù xiān yóule, mǔqīn lìng jià, wǒ jiù hěn shǎo huíqùle

367
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:08,596
不过离家久了，还是会想家
But I sometimes get homesick
Bùguò lí jiā jiǔle, háishì huì xiǎng jiā

368
00:42:09,920 --> 00:42:14,597
听说你离家都十年了，你就一点都不想家啊？
I heard that you left home ten years ago, don't you ever miss it?
Tīng shuō nǐ lí jiā dōu shí niánle, nǐ jiù yīdiǎn dōu bùxiǎng jiā a?

369
00:42:16,040 --> 00:42:17,951
有没有想过回去？
Ever thought about going back?
Yǒu méiyǒu xiǎngguò huíqù?

370
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:20,879
还没有
No, I haven't
Hái méiyǒu

371
00:42:25,520 --> 00:42:29,669
晓天出生以后没带他回去见过爷爷吗？
Are you telling me that Xiaotian's never met his grandfather?
Xiǎo tiān chūshēng yǐhòu mò dài tā huíqù jiànguò yéyé ma?

372
00:42:44,520 --> 00:42:47,637
来，多吃一点，菜都凉了
Eat up, the food is getting cold
Lái, duō chī yīdiǎn, cài dōu liángle

373
00:42:49,640 --> 00:42:50,595
方正说…
Fangzheng said...
Fāngzhèng shuō…

374
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:53,751
你以前养过一匹马
that you owned a horse before
Nǐ yǐqián yǎngguò yī pǐ mǎ

375
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:59,159
普通人家，很少会养马，是吧？真的少见啊
It's rare for most families to own horses, don't you think?
Pǔtōng rénjiā, hěn shǎo huì yǎng mǎ, shì ba? Zhēn de shǎojiàn a

376
00:43:00,520 --> 00:43:02,078
是怎么样子的马呢？
What kind of horse?
Shì zěnme yàngzi de mǎ ne?

377
00:43:07,600 --> 00:43:08,589
对…
Yes...
Duì…

378
00:43:11,640 --> 00:43:13,232
我有过一匹马
I had a horse once
Wǒ yǒuguò yī pǐ mǎ

379
00:43:16,320 --> 00:43:18,276
但后来被我爹杀了
But my father killed it
Dàn hòulái bèi wǒ diē shāle

380
00:43:24,600 --> 00:43:27,353
我爹看见我跟马的感情很好
My father saw that I loved my horse
Wǒ diē kànjiàn wǒ gēn mǎ de gǎnqíng hěn hǎo

381
00:43:30,080 --> 00:43:31,559
就把马杀了
so he killed it
Jiù bǎ mǎ shāle

382
00:43:33,960 --> 00:43:35,393
然后给我吃
and fed me its flesh
Ránhòu gěi wǒ chī

383
00:43:39,840 --> 00:43:41,353
吃的时候我不知道
I ate it without knowing
Chī de shíhòu wǒ bù zhīdào

384
00:43:46,120 --> 00:43:47,155
然后他说
Then he said
Ránhòu tā shuō

385
00:43:49,160 --> 00:43:52,596
如果我连最心爱的马都可以吃掉的话
if I could stomach eating my horse
Rúguǒ wǒ lián zuì xīn'ài de mǎ dōu kěyǐ chī diào dehuà

386
00:43:56,120 --> 00:43:58,350
这世上就没什么好怕的了
I could face anything
Zhè shìshàng jiù méishénme hǎo pà dele

387
00:44:00,440 --> 00:44:02,590
再没什么事情可以难倒我了
nothing could defeat me
Zài méishénme shìqíng kěyǐ nán dǎo wǒle

388
00:44:09,560 --> 00:44:11,915
你说这样的家还想回去吗？
Would you go back to a place like that?
Nǐ shuō zhèyàng de jiā hái xiǎng huíqù ma?

389
00:44:27,720 --> 00:44:28,789
好吃吗？
Hào chī ma?
Did it taste good?

390
00:44:32,200 --> 00:44:33,599
不…好…吃
Not at all
Bù…hǎo…chī

391
00:44:46,120 --> 00:44:47,235
不早了
It's late
Bù zǎole

392
00:44:53,680 --> 00:44:54,749
哎呦，这么晚了
Yes, it's late
Āi yōu, zhème wǎnle

393
00:44:55,200 --> 00:44:58,829
那我…先去睡
I could... have a shower first
Nà wǒ…xiān qù shuì

394
00:44:59,440 --> 00:45:03,838
我睡楼上是吗？没关系，慢慢吃
Am I sleeping upstairs? I'll find my own way, please continue
Wǒ shuì lóu shàng shì ma? Méiguānxì, màn man chī

395
00:45:22,040 --> 00:45:29,077
杀手暴恹之气多年下来，脸色青白，眼珠子也会变成绿阴阴的
After years of killing, the murderer's face becomes pale, the eyes turn green
Shāshǒu bào yān zhī qì duōnián xia lái, liǎnsè qīngbái, yǎnzhū zi yě huì biàn chéng lǜyīn yīn de

396
00:45:30,200 --> 00:45:35,035
而且全身有一股阴森森冷冰冰的杀气
even the air around the body grows cold
Érqiě quánshēn yǒuyī gǔ yīnsēn sēn lěngbīngbīng de shāqì

397
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:48,075
怎么眼珠子不是绿色的？
Why aren't your eyes green?
Zěnme yǎnzhū zi bùshì lǜsè de?

398
00:45:53,160 --> 00:45:58,359
喝不喝水？我有点渴了
Thirsty? I'm thirsty
Hē bù hē shuǐ? Wǒ yǒudiǎn kěle

399
00:46:08,960 --> 00:46:14,150
凡吾族子弟达成人之年
Sons of the clan you've reached the age of adulthood
Fán wú zú zǐdì dáchéng rén zhī nián

400
00:46:14,680 --> 00:46:21,592
从此容体正而后礼义备，以正君臣
From this day forth you must dress and conduct yourself as men, protect and serve the emperor
Cóngcǐ róngtǐ zhèng érhòu lǐ yì bèi, yǐ zhèng jūnchén

404
00:46:41,880 --> 00:46:44,189
刘天乐  -更衣之后，就不再是小孩儿了
With these clothes, you become a man
Liútiānyuè  -gēngyī zhīhòu, jiù bù zài shì xiǎo hái'érle

405
00:47:14,120 --> 00:47:22,353
一拜   再拜   上香
Bow, and again, offer incense
Yī bài   zài bài   shàng xiāng

406
00:47:41,160 --> 00:47:44,519
你刚才好像很感动，是吗？
You looked guite moved, were you?
Nǐ gāngcái hǎoxiàng hěn gǎndòng, shì ma?

407
00:47:49,160 --> 00:47:56,513
到底什么事情，会让一个人离家十年连自己的姓名都换掉了？
I've always wondered, why you left home and changed your name, what happened ten years ago?
Dàodǐ shénme shìqíng, huì ràng yīgè rén lí jiā shí nián lián zìjǐ de xìngmíng dū huàn diàole?

408
00:47:58,560 --> 00:47:59,913
人不可以改变吗？
I needed a change
Rén bù kěyǐ gǎibiàn ma?

409
00:48:03,160 --> 00:48:04,878
曾经我抓过一个少年
I caught a young thief once
Céngjīng wǒ zhuāguò yīgè shàonián

410
00:48:05,400 --> 00:48:10,078
就是我以为他会改变，所以决心放过了他
I thought he would reform, and let him go home
Jiùshì wǒ yǐwéi tā huì gǎibiàn, suǒyǐ juéxīn fàngguòle tā

411
00:48:11,640 --> 00:48:14,279
但是没想到，他回去以后
I never imagined that
Dànshì méi xiǎngdào, tā huíqù yǐhòu

412
00:48:14,840 --> 00:48:16,671
竟然毒死他父母
he would poison his own parents
Jìngrán dú sǐ tā fùmǔ

413
00:48:18,040 --> 00:48:19,029
你说
Tell me
Nǐ shuō

414
00:48:19,800 --> 00:48:26,593
那个少年跑掉改名换姓就真的可以变成另一个人？我不晓得
If he had run away and changed his name, could he really have changed? I don't think so
Nàgè shàonián pǎo diào gǎimíng huàn xìng jiù zhēn de kěyǐ biàn chéng lìng yīgè rén? Wǒ bù xiǎodé

415
00:48:34,360 --> 00:48:35,918
你想抓我
You want to arrest me
Nàgè shàonián pǎo diào gǎimíng huàn xìng jiù zhēn de kěyǐ biàn chéng lìng yīgè rén? Wǒ bù xiǎodé

416
00:48:44,600 --> 00:48:46,158
我是个杀人犯！
I was a convicted murderer
Wǒ shìgè shārén fàn!

417
00:48:50,400 --> 00:48:52,550
我曾在荆州坐牢十年
I was in Lianzhou prison for ten years
Wǒ céng zài jīngzhōu zuòláo shí nián

418
00:48:56,200 --> 00:49:01,638
那时候我还在龚家庄，我爹是个屠夫
I was originally from Gong Village, my father was a butcher
Nà shíhòu wǒ hái zài gōngjiāzhuāng, wǒ diē shìgè túfū

419
00:49:07,520 --> 00:49:13,679
当时，有另一户屠夫向我们家借了钱，却无力偿还
another butcher borrowed money from us... but never paid us back
Dāngshí, yǒu lìng yī hù túfū xiàng wǒmen jiā jièle qián, què wúlì chánghuán

420
00:49:13,880 --> 00:49:20,436
爹说，人跟畜牲其实没什么两样
My father said, men are no different from animals
Diē shuō, rén gēn chù sheng qíshí méishénme liǎngyàng

421
00:49:21,360 --> 00:49:23,157
这个人比畜牲还贱
But this man is lower than an animal
Zhège rén bǐ chù sheng hái jiàn

422
00:49:25,720 --> 00:49:26,948
因为他贪！
because he's greedy
Yīnwèi tā tān!

423
00:49:29,840 --> 00:49:31,717
然后爹就拿肉刀给我
My father handed me his cleaver
Ránhòu diē jiù ná ròu dāo gěi wǒ

424
00:49:33,840 --> 00:49:39,718
我一刀一刀的宰下去，一点感觉都没有
I hacked the man to death, I felt nothing
Wǒ yīdāo yīdāo de zǎi xiàqù, yīdiǎn gǎnjué dōu méiyǒu

425
00:49:42,400 --> 00:49:43,913
突然我停下来
I suddenly froze
Túrán wǒ tíng xiàlái

426
00:49:46,520 --> 00:49:48,351
我听见那屠夫的儿子在哭
I heard the man's son crying, the child was still alive
Wǒ tīngjiàn nà túfū de érzi zài kū

427
00:49:51,920 --> 00:49:55,313
那孩子没断气，他一直看着我
He was staring at me
Nà háizi méi duànqì, tā yīzhí kànzhe wǒ

428
00:50:01,880 --> 00:50:06,590
原来我爹是错的！人，不是畜牲
my father was wrong, humans are not animals
Yuánlái wǒ diē shì cuò de! Rén, bùshì chù sheng

429
00:50:09,400 --> 00:50:12,836
你杀了人，不可能只判十年
A murder sentence should be more than ten years
Nǐ shāle rén, bù kěnéng zhǐ pàn shí nián

430
00:50:15,080 --> 00:50:17,355
十年前有次大赦
There was an amnesty ten years ago
Shí nián qián yǒu cì dàshè

431
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:27,116
我知道如果要抹掉过去
I knew I had to change
Wǒ zhīdào rúguǒ yào mǒ diào guòqù

432
00:50:28,440 --> 00:50:31,159
就一定要离开家乡，重新来过
Jiù yīdìng yào líkāi jiāxiāng, chóngxīn láiguò
I had to leave my hometown to live a new life

433
00:50:34,040 --> 00:50:35,632
我要做刘金喜
I needed to be Liu Jinxi
Jiù yīdìng yào líkāi jiāxiāng, chóngxīn láiguò

434
00:50:41,360 --> 00:50:42,793
我差一点点就可以了
I almost succeeded
Wǒ chà yī diǎndiǎn jiù kěyǐle

435
00:50:43,040 --> 00:50:45,190
哎，爹，买卖就要开始了！
Father, the market is open!
Āi, diē, mǎimài jiù yào kāishǐle!

436
00:50:49,680 --> 00:50:58,589
请你离开这里，好吗？
Please leave us alone
Qǐng nǐ líkāi zhèlǐ, hǎo ma?

437
00:51:01,960 --> 00:51:03,678
爹，咱们快走啊
Father, we need to hurry!
Diē, zánmen kuàizǒu a

438
00:51:03,800 --> 00:51:05,870
徐百九，你也跟我们一起去吧
Xu Baijiu, you should come too!
Xúbǎijiǔ, nǐ yě gēn wǒmen yīqǐ qù ba

439
00:51:06,520 --> 00:51:08,988
好，马上来！
I'll be right there
Hǎo, mǎshàng lái!

441
00:51:15,500 --> 00:51:16,300
快点！
Hurry!
Kuài diǎn!

442
00:51:18,120 --> 00:51:21,069
来了，走吧
Hurry!, Let's go
Láile, zǒu ba

443
00:51:52,080 --> 00:51:54,878
怎么会他的气场比一般人强
He's surrounded by an energy field?
Zěnme huì tā de qì chǎng bǐ yībānrén qiáng

444
00:51:55,040 --> 00:51:58,431
他发出的外气，连苍蝇都飞不近身
He's radiating Qi energy, repelling even the flies
Tā fāchū de wài qì, lián cāngyíng dōu fēi bù jìn shēn

445
00:51:59,280 --> 00:52:00,759
他骗你的！
He lied to you!
Tā piàn nǐ de!

446
00:52:02,520 --> 00:52:06,392
哪里有普通屠夫的儿子有这么高的功夫？
How could a common butcher develop... such powerful Qi?
Nǎ li yǒu pǔtōng túfū de érzi yǒu zhème gāo de gōngfū?

447
00:52:07,240 --> 00:52:10,676
试一下，保证砍不进去
Take this, I guarantee it won't cut him
Shì yīxià, bǎozhèng kǎn bù jìnqù

448
00:52:53,240 --> 00:52:54,639
哪个说砍不进去的？
You told me it wouldn't cut?
Nǎge shuō kǎn bù jìnqù de?

449
00:52:58,920 --> 00:53:07,917
三颗杉树一样尖，哪个欺负刘金喜
Pine trees are prickly, whoever dares to bully Liu Jinxi?
Sān kē shān shù yīyàng jiān, nǎge qīfù liújīnxǐ

450
00:53:08,160 --> 00:53:17,249
欺负金喜我不肯，官司有打眼眉前
Now you have to deal with me, you frown when you've done wrong
Qīfù jīn xǐ wǒ bù kěn, guānsī yǒu dǎ yǎnméi qián

450
00:53:17,416 --> 00:53:21,332
月亮一出两头尖
Each new moon has two prongs
Yuèliàng yī chū liǎngtóu jiān

451
00:53:21,400 --> 00:53:23,436
徐某你为什么来这村？
Xu Baijiu, go away!
Xú mǒu nǐ wèishéme lái zhè cūn?

452
00:53:23,560 --> 00:53:27,678
想要看你无船渡
No boat will ferry you along
Xiǎng yào kàn nǐ wú chuándù

453
00:53:27,880 --> 00:53:31,953
写信谈心无邮传
Your letters will have no name
Xiě xìn tánxīn wú yóu chuán

454
00:53:32,440 --> 00:53:36,069
你说你，讨厌不讨厌？
Have you no shame?
Nǐ shuō nǐ, tǎoyàn bù tǎoyàn?

455
00:53:53,520 --> 00:53:54,953
我都打听清楚了
I've verified the facts
Wǒ dū dǎtīng qīngchǔle

456
00:53:55,840 --> 00:53:58,195
荆州从来没有什么龚家庄的
There's no Gong Village in Lianzhou
Jīngzhōu cónglái méiyǒu shé me gōngjiāzhuāng de

457
00:54:00,200 --> 00:54:04,073
荆州所有的屠夫里也没有什么姓龚的
There were no butchers in Lianzhou, with a last name Gong
Jīngzhōu suǒyǒu de túfū lǐ yě méiyǒu shé me xìng gōng de

458
00:54:05,760 --> 00:54:10,389
不过十年前倒是有一宗屠夫家的灭门案
But ten years ago a butcher's family was massacred
Bùguò shí nián qián dǎoshì yǒuyī zōng túfū jiā de mièmén àn

459
00:54:12,760 --> 00:54:14,432
一个姓张的屠夫
A butcher named Zhang
Yīgè xìng zhāng de túfū

460
00:54:14,720 --> 00:54:18,190
因为借了钱，却无力偿还，全家被杀了
borrowed money but didn't repay the loan
Yīnwèi jièle qián, què wúlì chánghuán, quánjiā bèi shāle

461
00:54:18,320 --> 00:54:22,714
后来被做成了肉馅，做成了包子分给村民吃
Their fest was used for savory bun filling, and distributed to unsuspecting villagers
Hòulái bèi zuò chéngle ròu xiàn, zuò chéngle bāozi fēn gěi cūnmín chī

462
00:54:24,040 --> 00:54:28,114
村民还说，从来没吃过这么香的包子
The villagers said they had never tasted anything so delicious
Cūnmín hái shuō, cónglái méi chīguò zhème xiāng de bāozi

463
00:54:29,320 --> 00:54:32,198
这事…你应该知道
You must be familiar with the case
Zhè shì…nǐ yīnggāi zhīdào

464
00:54:40,440 --> 00:54:42,715
怎么样，你没事吧？
Are you alright?
Zěnme yàng, nǐ méishì ba?

465
00:54:44,080 --> 00:54:45,399
没事
I'm fine, Captain
Méishì

466
00:54:45,640 --> 00:54:48,632
慢慢就好了，时间长了就适应了
You'll get used to it in time
Màn man jiù hǎole, shíjiān zhǎngle jiù shìyìngle

467
00:54:50,040 --> 00:54:51,359
我跟你说
Listen
Wǒ gēn nǐ shuō

468
00:54:51,560 --> 00:54:55,553
这个七十二地煞，昔日是西夏族的
The 72 Demons are the last surviving Tanguts
Zhège qīshí'èr dìshà, xīrì shì xīxià zú de

469
00:54:56,400 --> 00:54:59,710
以前跟我们中原人一样知书达理
They used to be civilized, like us
Yǐqián gēn wǒmen zhōngyuán rén yīyàng zhīshūdálǐ

470
00:55:00,280 --> 00:55:03,511
当年整族八十万人被屠杀精光
But after the massacre of 800,000 Tanguts
Dāngnián zhěng zú bāshí wàn rén bèi túshā jīngguāng

471
00:55:04,080 --> 00:55:09,158
如今变成三不像，割鲜而食，死而不葬
The survivors became savages, they ate raw meat and left their dead unburied
Rújīn biàn chéng sān bù xiàng, gē xiān ér shí, sǐ ér bù zàng

472
00:55:09,440 --> 00:55:13,310
活着，就是为了报那八十万的仇
Hunger for revenge, is what keeps them alive
Huózhe, jiùshì wèile bào nà bāshí wàn de chóu

473
00:55:13,960 --> 00:55:15,678
这也是我们的报应吧
I guess it's karma
Zhè yěshì wǒmen de bàoyìng ba

474
00:55:17,920 --> 00:55:22,079
那个案子之后，七十二地煞的二当家的就失踪了
After this killing... Tang Long, the second in command, went missing
Nàgè àn zǐ zhīhòu, qīshí'èr dìshà de èr dāngjiāde jiù shīzōngle

475
00:55:23,200 --> 00:55:28,672
刘金喜来这里，大概也快十年了吧
Liu Jinxi has lived here for exactly ten years, hasn't he?
Liú jīn xǐlái zhèlǐ, dàgài yě kuài shí niánle ba

476
00:55:33,360 --> 00:55:34,713
他就是唐龙！
So he is Tang Long!
Tā jiùshì táng lóng!

477
00:55:48,720 --> 00:55:52,234
你的确失踪十年，但你没坐过牢
You disappeared for 10 years but you were never imprisoned
Nǐ díquè shīzōng shí nián, dàn nǐ méi zuòguò láo

478
00:55:52,880 --> 00:55:56,678
你是杀了屠夫一家，但你不是屠夫的儿子
You Killed the butcher's family, you 're not a butcher's son
Nǐ shì shāle túfū yījiā, dàn nǐ bùshì túfū de érzi

479
00:55:57,600 --> 00:55:59,830
你是七十二地煞的二当家
You were the 72 Demons' second in command
Nǐ shì qīshí'èr dìshà de èr dāngjiā

480
00:56:01,840 --> 00:56:05,355
回县城，取牌票，捉拿疑犯！
I must return to the county to get a warrant for his arrest!
Huí xiànchéng, qǔ pái piào, zhuōná yífàn!

481
00:56:21,640 --> 00:56:24,200
徐百九，你要去哪儿？
Xu Baijiu, where are you going?
Xúbǎijiǔ, nǐ yào qù nǎ'er?

482
00:56:43,160 --> 00:56:44,434
你是不是要回县城？
Are you leaving?
Nǐ shì bùshì yào huí xiànchéng?

483
00:56:46,080 --> 00:56:47,433
是，是呀
Yes
Shì, shì ya

484
00:56:49,520 --> 00:56:51,112
这件事该告一段落了
I suppose your work here is done?
Zhè jiàn shì gāi gào yīduànluòle

485
00:56:58,280 --> 00:57:01,113
你的伤，好得快呀
You healed quickly
Nǐ de shāng, hǎo dé kuài ya

486
00:57:02,040 --> 00:57:05,279
大夫说如果再过半分就会伤及血管
The doctor said you nearly cut a major artery
Dàfū shuō rúguǒ zàiguò bàn fèn jiù huì shāng jí xiěguǎn

487
00:57:07,320 --> 00:57:08,799
恐怕就没救了
That would have killed me
Kǒngpà jiù méi jiùle

488
00:57:11,840 --> 00:57:13,239
你倒有运气啊
You were lucky
Nǐ dào yǒu yùnqì a

489
00:57:17,520 --> 00:57:19,078
还是你有运气
May be you're lucky?
Háishì nǐ yǒu yùnqì

490
00:57:28,560 --> 00:57:32,553
我知道有条捷径，我可以带你走
I know a shortcut, let me lead the way
Wǒ zhīdào yǒu tiáo jiéjìng, wǒ kěyǐ dài nǐ zǒu

491
00:57:33,080 --> 00:57:37,788
我怕你天黑之前赶不到凤城投栈，那就糟了
Otherwise, you won't make it to Feng County by nightfall, that would be a shame
Wǒ pà nǐ tiān hēi zhīqián gǎn bu dào fèng chéng tóu zhàn, nà jiù zāole

492
00:57:59,800 --> 00:58:01,518
这条捷径没有很多人知道
Few people know about this path
Zhè tiáo jiéjìng méiyǒu hěnduō rén zhīdào

493
00:58:04,160 --> 00:58:05,559
后来被我发现了
I came across it by accident
Hòulái bèi wǒ fāxiànle

494
00:58:07,520 --> 00:58:09,829
回去以后，你真的会销案吗？
Will you close the case after you leave here?
Huíqù yǐhòu, nǐ zhēn de huì xiāo'àn ma?

495
00:58:11,600 --> 00:58:14,388
会，会销案的
Yes, I will
Huì, huì xiāo'àn de

496
00:58:27,640 --> 00:58:28,993
你不信我
You don't believe me?
Nǐ bùxìn wǒ

497
00:58:59,040 --> 00:59:00,678
我们就在这儿分手
We part ways here
Wǒmen jiù zài zhè'er fēnshǒu

498
00:59:22,680 --> 00:59:27,439
一直向前走，大概半个时辰就会上大路
Keep going straight, after an hour you'll reach the main road
Yīzhí xiàng qián zǒu, dàgài bàn gè shíchén jiù huì shàng dàlù

499
00:59:28,960 --> 00:59:32,558
再走一会儿，就是凤城了
Keep walking, and you'll find Feng County
Zài zǒu yīhuǐ'er, jiùshì fèng chéngle

500
00:59:45,680 --> 00:59:47,193
你还不走？
What are you waiting for?
Nǐ hái bù zǒu?

501
00:59:48,200 --> 00:59:49,679
那我走了
Goodbye, then
Nà wǒ zǒule

502
01:00:45,240 --> 01:00:48,073
原来那条路真的能通往凤城
That road did lead to Feng County
Yuánlái nà tiáo lù zhēn de néng tōng wǎng fèng chéng

503
01:00:49,000 --> 01:00:50,513
为什么他不杀我？
Why didn't he kill me?
Wèishéme tā bù shā wǒ?

504
01:00:55,440 --> 01:00:58,512
徐百九，你跟了我十年了还会那么天真？
You've worked for me for ten years and still so naive?
Xúbǎijiǔ, nǐ gēnle wǒ shí niánle hái huì nàme tiānzhēn?

505
01:01:00,560 --> 01:01:02,312
班头，这次不一样
Captain, it's different this time
Bān tóu, zhè cì bù yīyàng

506
01:01:03,680 --> 01:01:06,399
我手下的捕快倒是有十几个
I could lend you the men under my command
Wǒ shǒuxià de bǔ kuài dǎoshì yǒu shí jǐ gè

507
01:01:07,320 --> 01:01:11,313
但现在能调遣的也就是褴褛枯瘠的尸骨
but they're just a bunch of cowards and bums
Dàn xiànzài néng diàoqiǎn de yě jiùshì lánlǚ kū jí de shīgǔ

508
01:01:12,320 --> 01:01:14,151
再不就是罪犯
Hire some outlaws
Zàibu jiùshì zuìfàn

509
01:01:14,280 --> 01:01:15,872
让罪犯抓罪犯…
but using criminals to stop a criminal...
Ràng zuìfàn zhuā zuìfàn…

510
01:01:16,920 --> 01:01:20,037
怕是那个捕快都没有这个胆子
is playing with fire
Pà shì nàgè bǔ kuài dōu méiyǒu zhège dǎnzi

511
01:01:20,760 --> 01:01:21,875
徐百九
Xu Baijiu
Xúbǎijiǔ

512
01:01:22,360 --> 01:01:24,032
我劝你还是收手
Just let it go
Wǒ quàn nǐ háishì shōu shǒu

513
01:01:24,120 --> 01:01:25,633
唐龙又不是通缉犯
Tang Long is not a wanted criminal
Táng lóng yòu bùshì tōngjī fàn

514
01:01:25,840 --> 01:01:27,876
你凭什么到我这来拿牌票？
why do you want a warrant?
Nǐ píng shénme dào wǒ zhè lái ná pái piào?

515
01:01:28,120 --> 01:01:30,429
七十二地煞罪大滔天
The 72 Demons are notorious outlaws
Qīshí'èr dìshà zuì dà tāotiān

516
01:01:30,720 --> 01:01:32,870
唐龙是二当家，当然要抓
And Tang Long is their second in command
Táng lóng shì èr dāngjiā, dāngrán yào zhuā

517
01:01:33,600 --> 01:01:35,431
罪证，罪证？
Where's the proof?
Zuìzhèng, zuìzhèng?

518
01:01:36,960 --> 01:01:42,516
就算是你筹得那买牌票的钱，也怕你无命回
Even if you bribe the judge for a warrant, you're risking your life
Jiùsuàn shì nǐ chóu dé nà mǎi pái piào de qián, yě pà nǐ wú mìng huí

519
01:01:42,680 --> 01:01:43,874
那我就上禀州府
I'll report the judge!
Nà wǒ jiù shàng bǐng zhōu fǔ

520
01:01:44,040 --> 01:01:44,995
胡说！
Nonsense!
Húshuō!

521
01:01:45,120 --> 01:01:46,519
少废话，你要多少银子？
How much do you want?
Shǎo fèihuà, nǐ yào duōshǎo yínzi?

522
01:01:50,040 --> 01:01:51,268
二十两银子
20 taels of silver
Èrshí liǎng yínzi

523
01:01:51,920 --> 01:01:52,830
什么？
What?
Shénme?

524
01:01:53,920 --> 01:01:55,831
我一年的俸禄是四两
Where will I find that?
Wǒ yī nián de fènglù shì sì liǎng

525
01:01:55,960 --> 01:01:57,359
哪来二十两银子！
I only receive 4 taels a year!
Nǎ lái èrshí liǎng yínzi!

526
01:01:57,520 --> 01:01:59,112
今天办公时间到了
Business hours are over
Jīntiān bàngōng shíjiān dàole

527
01:02:00,080 --> 01:02:02,116
你把二十两银子凑齐了，再来找我吧
Come back to me, when you have the money
Nǐ bǎ èrshí liǎng yínzi còu qíle, zàilái zhǎo wǒ ba

528
01:02:13,840 --> 01:02:17,628
没想到我要求一个我最不想求的人
I never expected to need help from this person:
Méi xiǎngdào wǒ yāoqiú yīgè wǒ zuì bùxiǎng qiú de rén

529
01:02:18,400 --> 01:02:19,594
我的妻子
My wife
Wǒ de qīzi

530
01:02:50,040 --> 01:02:51,189
我一定还你
I'll pay you back
Wǒ yīdìng hái nǐ

531
01:03:05,960 --> 01:03:07,678
生意还好吗？
Is business good?
Shēngyì hái hǎo ma?

533
01:03:16,720 --> 01:03:19,280
我给岳父上柱香就走
I'll burn incense for your father
Wǒ gěi yuèfù shàng zhù xiāng jiù zǒu

534
01:03:21,160 --> 01:03:22,070
不必了
Don't bother
Bùbìle

535
01:03:24,840 --> 01:03:26,398
我怕爹会不高兴
I'm afraid father wouldn't like it
Wǒ pà diē huì bù gāoxìng

536
01:03:28,680 --> 01:03:32,234
他走时，叮嘱过的
Before he's passed away, he made it clear
Tā zǒushí, dīngzhǔguò de

537
01:03:36,560 --> 01:03:39,709
那你呢，还觉得我错？
What about you?
Nà nǐ ne, hái juédé wǒ cuò?

538
01:03:39,800 --> 01:03:40,835
还重要吗？
You still blame me? Does it matter?
Hái zhòngyào ma?

539
01:03:46,200 --> 01:03:47,952
我爹卖假药是不对
Father was wrong to sell fake medicine
Wǒ diē mài jiǎ yào shì bùduì

540
01:03:49,840 --> 01:03:50,989
可是那些药…
But the medicine...
Kěshì nàxiē yào…

541
01:03:52,440 --> 01:03:53,873
也不会害人性命
didn't cost any lives
Yě bù huì hài rén xìngmìng

542
01:03:56,560 --> 01:04:00,759
当初他跪在你面前，向你求饶
He got on his knees and begged for your mercy
Dāngchū tā guì zài nǐ miànqián, xiàng nǐ qiúráo

543
01:04:02,960 --> 01:04:04,598
你却仍然不放过他
you wouldn't let go
Nǐ què réngrán bù fàngguò tā

544
01:04:06,720 --> 01:04:08,153
你是什么心情？
What did it feel like?
Nǐ shì shénme xīnqíng?

545
01:04:08,280 --> 01:04:11,674
只要那个人犯了法，我就要抓
It wasn't up to me, it's the law
Zhǐyào nàgè rénfànle fǎ, wǒ jiù yào zhuā

546
01:04:14,360 --> 01:04:19,394
而且你爹是卖假药被抓，何必自杀呢？
He was only guilty of selling fake medicine, he didn't need to kill himself
Érqiě nǐ diē shì mài jiǎ yào bèi zhuā, hébì zìshā ne?

547
01:04:19,560 --> 01:04:22,269
我知道，你说过了
I know, you said it before
Wǒ zhīdào, nǐ shuōguòle

548
01:04:31,040 --> 01:04:33,156
我想你是不会原谅我了
You'll never forgive me
Wǒ xiǎng nǐ shì bù huì yuánliàng wǒle

549
01:04:36,320 --> 01:04:38,197
你觉得是吗？
you still don't understand
Nǐ juédé shì ma?

550
01:04:41,560 --> 01:04:47,116
不原谅，得心里还在乎！
Not forgiving, you'd have to still care!
Bù yuánliàng, dé xīnlǐ hái zàihū!

551
01:04:58,400 --> 01:05:01,836
到底法是不是真的比人重要？
Is the law really more important than humanity?
Dàodǐ fǎ shì bùshì zhēn de bǐ rén zhòngyào?

552
01:05:08,720 --> 01:05:12,116
班头，这究竟是个什么世道？
Captain, what has the world come to?
Bān tóu, zhè jiùjìng shìgè shénme shìdào?

553
01:05:12,360 --> 01:05:14,920
在什么世道，做什么样的人
Whatever the world has become
Zài shénme shìdào, zuò shénme yàng de rén

554
01:05:16,640 --> 01:05:19,393
你以为你自己可以做自己的主啊？
you have no choice but to be part of it
Nǐ yǐwéi nǐ zìjǐ kěyǐ zuò zìjǐ de zhǔ a?

555
01:05:40,640 --> 01:05:43,994
徐坤，你要带我去哪儿？  -不是去拿银子吗？
Tsu Kun, where're you taking me? -Where's my reward?
Xú kūn, nǐ yào dài wǒ qù nǎ'er?  -Bùshì qù ná yínzi ma?

556
01:05:44,560 --> 01:05:46,516
你的话，自己跟教主说
Whatever you have to say, tell Master yourself
Nǐ dehuà, zìjǐ gēn jiàozhǔ shuō

557
01:05:48,520 --> 01:05:49,635
你是说…
Are you saying
Nǐ shì shuō…

558
01:05:50,200 --> 01:05:55,310
我们的唐龙就在你说的那条村子里？是！
Tang Long is in the village that you mentioned? Yes!
Our Tang Long is in the village you said? Yes!

559
01:05:55,400 --> 01:05:56,515
你还说…
And...
Nǐ hái shuō…

560
01:05:56,880 --> 01:06:00,670
唐龙现在有两个儿子了？是！
he has two sons? Yes!
Táng lóng xiànzài yǒu liǎng gè er zi le? Shì!

561
01:06:00,880 --> 01:06:05,352
一个是亲生的，一个是他妻子以前和别的男人生的
One is his, one is from his wife's previous marriage
Yīgè shì qīnshēng de, yīgè shì tā qī zǐ yǐqián hé bié de nánrén shēng de

562
01:06:07,280 --> 01:06:08,759
你告诉我…
Are you telling me this...
Nǐ gàosù wǒ…

563
01:06:08,920 --> 01:06:13,835
是因为你知道我想知道唐龙的行踪？
because you think I want information about Tang Long?
Shì yīnwèi nǐ zhīdào wǒ xiǎng zhīdào táng lóng de xíngzōng?

564
01:06:15,240 --> 01:06:17,276
徐坤，什么意思？
Tsu Kun, what's going on?
Xú kūn, shénme yìsi?

565
01:06:31,680 --> 01:06:32,908
是…是…  -怎么样？
Answer me
Shì…shì…  -zěnme yàng?

566
01:06:33,120 --> 01:06:38,040
你不向三十六天罡告密也不去黑龙帮告密
You didn't go to the 36 Constellations, you didn't go to the Black Dragon Gang
Nǐ bù xiàng sānshíliù tiāngāng gàomì yě bù qù hēilóng bāng gàomì

772
01:06:38,250 --> 01:06:40,165
偏偏来到这里
Instead, you came here
Piānpiān lái dào zhèlǐ

567
01:06:40,600 --> 01:06:45,352
是因为你知道，唐龙跟我们的关系最密切
Because you know, we have a connection with Tang Long
Shì yīnwèi nǐ zhīdào, táng lóng gēn wǒmen de guānxì zuì mìqiè

568
01:06:46,040 --> 01:06:47,792
是不是？
True?
Shì bùshì?

569
01:06:48,760 --> 01:06:50,193
不，不
No, no
Bù, bù

570
01:06:50,960 --> 01:06:53,635
教主误会了…不是这样…
Master... it's not... it's not what you think
Jiàozhǔ wùhuìle…bùshì zhèyàng…

571
01:06:55,240 --> 01:06:58,198
徐坤…救我…救我呀…
Tsu Kun, help me
Xú kūn…jiù wǒ…jiù wǒ ya…

573
01:07:03,200 --> 01:07:08,071
你告诉他，唐龙是我什么人
Tell him, who Tang Long is
Nǐ gàosù tā, táng lóng shì wǒ shénme rén

574
01:07:09,040 --> 01:07:12,709
唐龙是教主的亲生儿子！
Tang Long... is the son of our Master!
Táng lóng shì jiàozhǔ de qīnshēng érzi!

575
01:07:16,560 --> 01:07:21,951
你来告密，是要我亲手杀了自己的儿子
You came here with the information so that I would kill my own son
Nǐ lái gàomì, shì yào wǒ qīnshǒu shāle zìjǐ de érzi

576
01:07:22,760 --> 01:07:27,234
你，你好大的胆！
You...
Nǐ lái gàomì, shì yào wǒ qīnshǒu shāle zìjǐ de érzi

577
01:07:40,800 --> 01:07:44,071
你们说，我该不该把唐龙杀掉？
Tell me, should I kill Tang Long?
Nǐmen shuō, wǒ gāi bù gāi bǎ táng lóng shā diào?

578
01:07:46,920 --> 01:07:51,234
怎么样，我该不该把唐龙杀掉？
Well? Should I kill him?
Nǐmen shuō, wǒ gāi bù gāi bǎ táng lóng shā diào?

579
01:07:55,000 --> 01:07:56,877
你们没一个像唐龙
None of you can match him
Nǐmen méi yīgè xiàng táng lóng

580
01:07:57,960 --> 01:08:01,236
没有一个像唐龙！
Méiyǒu yīgè xiàng táng lóng!
None of you can match Tang Long!

581
01:08:02,000 --> 01:08:05,676
教主的意思是让唐龙回来！
Master wants to... bring Tang Long back!
Jiàozhǔ de yìsi shì ràng táng lóng huílái!

583
01:08:55,640 --> 01:08:58,076
你以前是种地的吗？  -是啊！
Did you ever work the land? -I did!
Nǐ yǐqián shì zhòng dì de ma?  -Shì a!

584
01:08:59,200 --> 01:09:00,315
他们念的什么？
Tāmen niàn de shénme?
What are they reciting?

585
01:09:02,560 --> 01:09:05,675
他们在求土地公保佑，为小生灵超度
They're praying for souls, to be released from purgatory
Tāmen zài qiú tǔdì gōng bǎoyòu, wèi xiǎo shēnglíng chāodù

586
01:09:06,280 --> 01:09:10,392
你想啊，一翻土肯定会伤害到里面的小生命了
You see, when you till the earth you can't avoid harming the small creatures in it
Nǐ xiǎng a, yī fān tǔ kěndìng huì shānghài dào lǐmiàn de xiǎo shēngmìngle

587
01:09:40,760 --> 01:09:46,879
金喜英勇杀贼的事迹，我们今天将记载在族谱上
Jīn xǐ yīngyǒng shā zéi de shìjì, wǒmen jīntiān jiāng jìzǎi zài zúpǔ shàng
Jinxi performed a brave deed by killing two criminals we make a record of Jinxi's great deed

588
01:09:47,600 --> 01:09:52,350
金喜为人一向正直，乃是本村之福
Jinxi is a man of integrity, his bravery and kindness
Jīn xǐ yīngyǒng shā zéi de shìjì, wǒmen jīntiān jiāng jìzǎi zài zúpǔ shàng

589
01:09:53,520 --> 01:10:00,080
今次的功德将长留族谱，成家族光荣
are a blessing to us and an example for our youth
Jīn cì de gōngdé jiāng zhǎng liú zúpǔ, chéng jiāzú guāngróng

590
01:10:00,080 --> 01:10:03,795
为日后族人，学习的典范！
We will remember, and be inspired!
Wèi rìhòu zúrén, xuéxí de diǎnfàn!

591
01:10:19,280 --> 01:10:22,352
见了十三娘，还不下跪
Go down on your knees
Jiànle shísān niáng, hái bù xià guì

592
01:10:25,400 --> 01:10:26,879
跪下！
Kneel!
Guì xià!

593
01:10:29,560 --> 01:10:31,039
我是刘金喜
I am Liu Jinxi
Wǒ shì liújīnxǐ

594
01:10:34,560 --> 01:10:35,834
刘金喜？
Liu Jinxi?
Liújīnxǐ?

596
01:10:46,760 --> 01:10:48,709
你认不认？  -爹…
Tell the truth! -Father!
Nǐ rèn bù rèn?  -Diē…

597
01:10:49,920 --> 01:10:51,273
你认不认？
Who are you?
Nǐ rèn bù rèn?

598
01:11:01,240 --> 01:11:04,793
我跟儿子说话，你们吵什么？
This is a family matter so shut up!
Wǒ gēn er zi shuōhuà, nǐmen chǎo shénme?

599
01:11:05,320 --> 01:11:07,550
吵什么吵，闭嘴！
Shut up!
Chǎo shénme chǎo, bì zuǐ!

600
01:11:11,800 --> 01:11:13,074
不许吵！
Be quiet!
Bùxǔ chǎo!

601
01:13:06,400 --> 01:13:08,231
你还说你不是唐龙
You deny you're Tang Long
Nǐ hái shuō nǐ bùshì táng lóng

602
01:13:17,160 --> 01:13:20,668
我家着火了，着火了！ 赶快救火…
My house is on fire! Help!
Wǒjiā zháohuǒle, zháohuǒle! Gǎnkuài jiùhuǒ…

603
01:14:31,800 --> 01:14:33,358
我不会跟你回去
I'm not going back
Wǒ bù huì gēn nǐ huíqù

604
01:14:33,720 --> 01:14:37,948
你知道是谁要你回去，他是不会放过你的！
You know that "he" wants you back, he won't give up!
Nǐ zhīdào shì shéi yào nǐ huíqù, tā shì bù huì fàngguò nǐ de!

605
01:17:30,800 --> 01:17:37,076
你是唐龙，你还是唐龙！
You are Tang Long, you still are!
Nǐ shì táng lóng, nǐ háishì táng lóng!

606
01:18:29,400 --> 01:18:30,628
给你倒杯水
I'll get you some water
Gěi nǐ dào bēi shuǐ

607
01:18:38,160 --> 01:18:41,118
村长说，要我们大家明天都躲到天寨去
The chief told us to shelter in the fortress
Cūn zhǎng shuō, yào wǒmen dàjiā míngtiān dū duǒ dào tiān zhài qù

608
01:18:41,880 --> 01:18:45,271
所以我在收拾东西，我把你东西也都收拾好了
That's why I'm packing, I've already packed your belongings
Suǒyǐ wǒ zài shōushí dōngxī, wǒ bǎ nǐ dōngxī yě dū shōushí hǎole

609
01:18:46,680 --> 01:18:48,033
对…
Good
Duì…

610
01:18:49,800 --> 01:18:51,279
什么意思？
What do you mean?
Shénme yìsi?

611
01:18:52,240 --> 01:18:54,037
我不能跟你们上天寨
I can't go with you
Wǒ bùnéng gēn nǐmen shàngtiān zhài

612
01:18:54,160 --> 01:18:57,396
那我们走，我们不去天寨，我们…我们…
So we're not going either, we should...
Nà wǒmen zǒu, wǒmen bù qù tiān zhài, wǒmen…wǒmen…

613
01:18:57,840 --> 01:19:01,319
我们逃到别的地方去，我们离开这里好不好？
we should leave and start a new life somewhere else
Wǒmen táo dào bié dì dìfāng qù, wǒmen líkāi zhèlǐ hǎobù hǎo?

614
01:19:01,400 --> 01:19:03,868
没用的，阿玉，没用的
it's useless...
Méi yòng de, āyù, méi yòng de

615
01:19:04,240 --> 01:19:06,037
你现在不可以这样说
How can you say that?
Nǐ xiànzài bù kěyǐ zhèyàng shuō

616
01:19:07,920 --> 01:19:09,000
来，先喝口水
Have some water
Lái, xiān hē kǒushuǐ

617
01:19:10,000 --> 01:19:13,233
已经很晚了，你不可以这样说，已经…
Don't say that
Yǐjīng hěn wǎnle, nǐ bù kěyǐ zhèyàng shuō, yǐjīng…

618
01:19:14,160 --> 01:19:16,310
现在说这些都已经太晚了，你知不知道？
It's too late, do you understand?
Xiànzài shuō zhèxiē dōu yǐjīng tài wǎnle, nǐ zhī bù zhīdào?

619
01:19:16,520 --> 01:19:18,670
谢谢你让我当了十年的刘金喜
Thanks for letting me be Liu Jinxi
Xièxiè nǐ ràng wǒ dāngle shí nián de liújīnxǐ

620
01:19:20,440 --> 01:19:22,158
但我不是刘金喜
But I'm not Liu Jinxi
Dàn wǒ bùshì liújīnxǐ

621
01:20:18,440 --> 01:20:19,634
金喜…
Jinxi
Jīn xǐ…

622
01:20:21,000 --> 01:20:25,634
如果那天在河边，你遇到的是另一个女人
That day by the pond, if the woman you met hadn't been me
Rúguǒ nèitiān zài hé biān, nǐ yù dào de shì lìng yīgè nǚrén

623
01:20:30,720 --> 01:20:32,870
你是否一样会留下来？
Would you have stayed?
Nǐ shìfǒu yīyàng huì liú xiàlái?

624
01:21:12,680 --> 01:21:14,910
大人，放过他们吧…
Sir, spare my children
Dàrén, fàngguò tāmen ba…

625
01:21:15,040 --> 01:21:18,271
你杀我吧，跟孩子没关系
Kill me if you must! They're innocent
Nǐ shā wǒ ba, gēn háizi méiguānxì

626
01:21:18,680 --> 01:21:24,000
大人，我求求您了…大人…
Sir, I beg you
Dàrén, wǒ qiú qiú nínle…dàrén…

631
01:23:52,920 --> 01:23:53,955
怎么回事？
What happened?
Zěnme huí shì?

632
01:23:56,600 --> 01:23:59,068
会不会是七十二地煞的人来过？
It must be the 72 Demons
Huì bù huì shì qīshí'èr dìshà de rén láiguò?

633
01:24:20,800 --> 01:24:24,871
现在不好办，我们抓了唐龙七十二地煞也会中途拦截
It doesn't look good, even if we capture Tang Long, the Demons might still ambush us
Xiànzài bù hǎo bàn, wǒmen zhuāle táng lóng qīshí'èr dìshà yě huì zhōngtú lánjié

634
01:24:25,080 --> 01:24:28,072
他们一定不会罢休，会回来的
Nothing will stop them
Tāmen yīdìng bù huì bàxiū, huì huílái de

635
01:24:28,360 --> 01:24:32,233
反正是这样，就让他们互相厮杀，杀精光了我们才进来
we should just let them kill each other and return later
Fǎnzhèng shì zhèyàng, jiù ràng tāmen hùxiāng sīshā, shā jīngguāngle wǒmen cái jìnlái

636
01:24:32,520 --> 01:24:34,317
杀清光了才进来有什么用啊？
What for, if he's dead?
Shā qīngguāngle cái jìnlái yǒu shé me yòng a?

637
01:24:34,440 --> 01:24:37,079
你就是把他抓回去不也是一死啊？
He'll receive a death sentence anyway
Nǐ jiùshì bǎ tā zhuā huíqù bù yěshì yīsǐ a?

638
01:24:37,560 --> 01:24:39,790
徐百九，你究竟想怎样啊？
Xu Baijiu, what do you really want?
Xúbǎijiǔ, nǐ jiùjìng xiǎng zěnyàng a?

639
01:24:46,600 --> 01:24:49,114
我就是要抓他回去受审啊
I must bring him to justice
Wǒ jiùshì yào zhuā tā huíqù shòushěn a

640
01:25:08,520 --> 01:25:10,033
不是不回来吗？
You promised never to return?
Bùshì bù huílái ma?

641
01:25:12,720 --> 01:25:14,438
这个就是唐龙？
Zhège jiùshì táng lóng?
Is this Tang Long?

642
01:25:18,920 --> 01:25:20,558
七十二地煞的唐龙
Tang Long of the 72 Demons
Zhège jiùshì táng lóng?

643
01:25:20,680 --> 01:25:22,113
他们一定会回来的
They will come back
Tāmen yīdìng huì huílái de

644
01:25:22,240 --> 01:25:24,956
徐百九，我们在外面，让他们互相残杀
Let's wait nearby, let them kill each other
Xúbǎijiǔ, wǒmen zài wàimiàn, ràng tāmen hùxiāng cánshā

645
01:25:26,120 --> 01:25:28,190
不行，全部要留下来！
No, we should all stay
Bùxíng, quánbù yào liú xiàlái!

646
01:25:28,320 --> 01:25:29,799
要留，你自已留吧
Stay if you want to
Yào liú, nǐ zìyǐ liú ba

647
01:25:29,920 --> 01:25:33,030
我们在外面等，等你们打完了，再来收尸  驾！
We're leaving, we'll return for the corpses
Wǒmen zài wàimiàn děng, děng nǐmen dǎ wánliǎo, zàilái shōushī  jià!

648
01:26:05,760 --> 01:26:07,034
那天在丛林…
The other day in the forest...
Nèitiān zài cónglín…

649
01:26:09,920 --> 01:26:11,319
你为什么不杀我？
why didn't you kill me?
Nǐ wèishéme bù shā wǒ?

650
01:26:14,800 --> 01:26:16,438
因为你说不会再回来
You promised never to return
Yīnwèi nǐ shuō bu huì zài huílái

651
01:26:21,080 --> 01:26:22,308
你信了？
And you believed me?
Nǐ xìnle?

652
01:26:29,840 --> 01:26:31,114
我信了
I did
Wǒ xìnle

653
01:26:34,840 --> 01:26:38,509
阿玉曾经跟我说，她说…
Ayu told me something, She said:
Āyù céngjīng gēn wǒ shuō, tā shuō…

654
01:26:39,720 --> 01:26:42,075
徐百九其实是个心肠很好的人
Xu Baijiu is a good man
Xúbǎijiǔ qíshí shì ge xīncháng hěn hǎo de rén

655
01:26:43,160 --> 01:26:44,957
可是他自己都不知道
He just doesn't know it
Kěshì tā zìjǐ dōu bù zhīdào

656
01:26:45,120 --> 01:26:46,439
没这回事
There is no such thing
Méi zhè huí shì

657
01:26:47,320 --> 01:26:49,515
世上没什么叫好人这回事
Good men don't exist
Shìshàng méishénme jiàohǎo rén zhè huí shì

658
01:26:57,280 --> 01:27:00,158
人的身体很奇妙，是可以骗人的
The human body is amazing, it can trick you
Rén de shēntǐ hěn qímiào, shì kěyǐ piàn rén de

659
01:27:01,040 --> 01:27:03,508
我就是要用你的身体来骗一次
I want to use your body to trick them
Wǒ jiùshì yào yòng nǐ de shēntǐ lái piàn yīcì

660
01:27:04,840 --> 01:27:07,959
唐龙，你一定要死！
Tang Long, you must die
Táng lóng, nǐ yīdìng yàosǐ!

661
01:27:17,960 --> 01:27:19,871
人的死分三个阶段
There are three stages of death:
Rén de sǐ fēn sān gè jiēduàn

662
01:27:20,600 --> 01:27:24,275
濒死期、死亡期和完全死亡
the brink, the degeneration and the final death
Bīn sǐqī, sǐwáng qī hé wánquán sǐwáng

663
01:27:24,760 --> 01:27:28,956
但濒死期表面看上去很多人都会误以为死亡
in the first stage, we appear dead, most people will be fooled
Dàn bīn sǐ qí biǎomiàn kàn shàngqù hěnduō rén dūhuì wù yǐwéi sǐwáng

664
01:27:29,080 --> 01:27:31,310
我就是要你先进入第一个阶段
I want you to enter this first stage
Wǒ jiùshì yào nǐ xiān jìnrù dì yī gè jiēduàn

665
01:27:32,840 --> 01:27:39,638
进入濒死期，人在深度昏迷状态不会武功的人是无法分辨的
you'll be in a coma, most people can't tell the difference
Jìnrù bīn sǐqī, rén zài shēndù hūnmí zhuàngtài bù huì wǔgōng de rén shì wúfǎ fēnbiàn de

666
01:27:39,760 --> 01:27:40,670
真的死啦？
He's dead?
Zhēn de sǐ la?

667
01:27:41,680 --> 01:27:45,114
但要骗过七十二地煞，我们就要再冒险！
But to trick the 72 demons, you need to enter
Dàn yào piànguò qīshí'èr dìshà, wǒmen jiù yào zài màoxiǎn!

668
01:27:45,520 --> 01:27:48,159
让你进入第二个阶段，死亡期
the more dangerous second stage
Ràng nǐ jìnrù dì èr gè jiēduàn, sǐwáng qī

669
01:27:49,560 --> 01:27:51,551
七十二地煞的人来的时候
When the demons arrive
Qīshí'èr dìshà de rén lái de shíhòu

670
01:27:51,960 --> 01:27:54,428
